app.alert(JSON.stringify(Object.getOwnPropertyNames(app.fs)));
```

All the PA schemes saying `no throw` — did the app change at all after you clicked OK? Did it navigate, flicker, or did Image5 change? Even a brief app switch would confirm a scheme was handled.

